issue.title: I can't see phone_3 in urban_qual

content.raw:
I cannot replicate this.  Just ran on my local `urban_circuit` checkout catkin-built native workspace and from the published docker image `osrf/subt-virtual-testbed` images and I was able to locate `phone_3` in both.

Here's a screenshot from the `osrf/subt-virtual-testbed` docker experiment:![Screenshot from 2020-01-02 17-23-55.png](data/bitbucket.org/repo/8ze6Mjd/images/3885496658-Screenshot_from_2020-01-02_17-23-55.png)
